10.0.9

This file is vendored (see docs/as.is/service-mode.md, "Non-obvious behavior / gotchas"
section) rather than served by ASP.NET Core's static-web-assets pipeline. It is tied to
the Microsoft.AspNetCore.App version above and can drift out of sync with whatever
version is actually resolved for the `Microsoft.AspNetCore.App` FrameworkReference at
build/run time on a given machine.

To refresh after upgrading the ASP.NET Core shared framework:
  1. Find the matching version under
     %userprofile%\.nuget\packages\microsoft.aspnetcore.app.internal.assets\<version>\_framework\blazor.web.js
  2. Copy it over wahlberg.maui/wwwroot/_framework/blazor.web.js
  3. Update the version number in this file
